            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>sea bass fillet[s]</strong>, skin side down with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper </strong>and cook for 5 min, then flip the sea bass and cook for 1 min further or until cooked through</p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked once it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1722006960891-x200.jpg",
