            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the reserved pot to a medium heat with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>chopped garlic </strong>and <strong>chopped tomato </strong>with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper </strong>and cook for 1-2 min or until fragrant</p><p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>spinach</strong> and <strong>drained giant couscous</strong> to the pot and give everything a good mix up until the spinach starts to wilt</p><p>Set aside until serving – this is your <strong>tomato & spinach couscous</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
